Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在...下雨呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不過 就算是下雨 小鳩也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土...鳩...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞得我滿身是泥啊!


Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:51.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:51.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:56.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:56.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:59.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:59.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:07.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:07.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:10.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:10.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:15.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:15.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:23.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:23.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:26.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:26.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:34.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:34.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:43.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:43.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:53.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:53.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:01.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:01.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

