Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[...雨的贈禮.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被弄髒了也沒關係的 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨會把這一切洗乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係個屁啊 那不是要淋得渾身濕透
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 清花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 真的可以住在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要小鳩你喜歡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 進裡面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你來介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲小姐是我的朋友 同時又是這座公寓的管理員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鳩小姐吧 初次見面 我叫三原千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼不清楚或是發愁的事儘管來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲 接下來就拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 小鳩 我要回保育園了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的 真是太感謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一會兒就去您那兒幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是總只顧著關照別人呢 清花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個很好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候應該說[今天起要受您關照了]才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起要在這裡關照您了 我是花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼是你關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李在大約幾點送到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有被褥之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 那先帶你去房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是座非常棒的建築呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 多謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好棒的房間啊 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 啊咧咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鳩...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幹得不錯啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是早就跟你說過了!在這裡我可只是個布偶啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多保育園要開園了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?差點忘了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快一點的話...要遲到了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒什麼 不過 這孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦 弄得你滿身是泥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這樣就弄乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感謝了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你比真是懂事多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有屋頂又可以在地上滾來滾去 非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在打掃衛生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做什麼好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著還幫她找住處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 不過她來了以後 孩子們也很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺負她可不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經吃過多少次苦頭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不管對誰都要加以防範才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了真好 而且明天保育園也休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要加油收集金平糖 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛還是大晴天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫你帶傘出門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來一時半會兒是不會停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有淋濕的份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好狡猾哦 只顧自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒有帶傘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話 請拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你吧 本來就是給客人用的傘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...等雨停了 一定送回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就等候您的光臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按小鳩來說 算是對應得不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在這裡收集想要被治癒的人的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上算是對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是人們經常出入的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩!會努力的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情報都沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借來的傘不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是誰拿錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被人擅自拿走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?傘可以擅自拿走的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是從蛋糕店借來的傘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 昨天的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘不見了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的傘借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很近的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果沒有傘的話 它不也會淋濕嗎 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 田所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總吃夜食的話 會更胖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 桂木你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不站住 揍你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住了也要揍吧 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!桂木!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算自己被淋濕 也要借傘給別人的人也有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鳩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦?臉上有榻榻米印兒...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情 臉上居然有榻榻米印兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲小姐肯定覺得我很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的傘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能找到我們學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向借給我傘的蛋糕店裡道歉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打聽到綠色水手服的話就是這所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生也很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是指這個布偶嗎 好奇怪的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫田所睦美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的頭髮 翹起來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪 哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我臉上還有榻榻米印兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不能算是安慰人...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 我還要晨練
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 剛才那個男孩子有點捉弄人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像籐本先生一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 遲到的話又要被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到1分23秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1...1分?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分的遲到也是遲到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你是不睡到時間就不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榻榻米的印兒已經沒有了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還從被子裡睡到外邊來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有被子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君又說你什麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他雖然有點冷冰冰的 不過不是個壞孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果他捉弄你的話就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你用拳頭教訓他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳...拳頭嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 像過去那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 難得天晴 去曬午睡用的被子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 我這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又要下雨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 帶傘了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有傘...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君有的吧 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等下還有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著我的傘走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我才不想和你打相合傘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(相合傘=男女二人同打一把傘)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相合傘?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指兩個人一起打同一把傘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清華老師說的好準啊 真的又下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拿錯的傘 被還回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?小鳩?又見面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 田所睦美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我睦美就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?是這樣啊 太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 睦美小姐又來買東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 劍道部的練習很辛苦所以肚子又餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃太多的話該胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是所謂相合傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美小姐...看上去很傷心...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼才能讓她變得有精神呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 這種事別人幫不上忙啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 請開開門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵到您了真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是管理員的女兒千帆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 初次見面 我叫花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有被褥吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 媽媽說"不嫌棄的話就請用吧"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說"雖然是以前用過的"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到一床被褥~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被治癒了有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要幫睦美小姐打起精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總 總之要加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你想做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得現在不要管那女孩的事比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話對你說 是關於睦美小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 請和睦美小姐也打相合傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"和睦美小姐也"算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一次 我看到睦美小姐一臉的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你和其他女生打相合傘的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我才沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我多管閒事的話 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 我希望睦美小姐能打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 和睦美小姐打相合傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對上次那女孩不大好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼嘛...不用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那女孩...不是在交往啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:20:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她說沒帶傘所以才一起走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美小姐 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦...走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等 我要被淋濕了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你離遠點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱怨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是事實嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說也...傘太小了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美小姐看上去也不是很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啦 那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呢 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是為了這個才去治癒那女孩的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想睦美小姐更精神一點才會去幫忙的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不管怎麼說 這就說明那女孩受傷的心被治癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖增加了就是最好的證據了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前途堪憂啊這...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那氣息是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼 琇一郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次總算完滿結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給個好分數也不為過嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要緊吧?五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土...鳩...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 五百祗先生 剛剛不是說要給個好分數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的錯我不是變得滿身泥水了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 雨會把這一切洗乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老子的怒火洗不掉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.99,0:24:28.96,預告,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話[...青葉的悸動.]


Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:07.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:15.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:23.40,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:32.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:42.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:49.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:53.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:24:01.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:05.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:10.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:14.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:27.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:07.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人們都是那麼想飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:15.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不過被重力所欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:23.40,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其實誰都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:32.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個孩子為什麼如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:42.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也許是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:49.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能對你說 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:53.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看見你的笑容 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:24:01.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來來往往中 變得愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:05.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:10.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:14.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:27.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜極而泣總是那麼不可思議
